  "description": {
    "zh": "我对当地混混之间的冲突一点都不感兴趣，两边都不准备搭理。但是既然你都来了，那我顺带找个事情给你做。\n\n任务很简单：在储备站军医院楼顶取一个货箱，把货物带到转移点去。搬箱子的时候千万小心点，还有中途不允许打开。这件货物可能会引起某些人的兴趣，所以我需要一个知道该怎么保持沉默的人来办得妥妥帖帖。你最好够格。",
    "en": "I am not interested in localized conflicts and I am not going to help either side. But since you are already here, I have a job for you.\n\nThe task is simple: pick up one cargo from the roof of the military hospital at the reserve base and deliver it to the transfer point. Be careful with the cargo and do not open the crate. This shipment might be of interest to certain people, so I need a man with special skills. Someone like you."
  },
